flowchart LR
    R[Reach] --> A[Align]
    A --> P[PreGraspHold]
    P --> D[Descend]
    D --> C[CloseHold]
    C --> L[LiftTest]
    L --> T[Transit]
    T --> M[MoveToPlaceAbove]
    M --> DP[DescendToPlace]
    DP --> O[Open]
    O --> RT[Retreat]
    RT --> DN[Done]

    D -.timeout/fail.-> R
    C -.grasp fail.-> R
    L -.drop/fail.-> R
    T -.lost grasp.-> R
    M -.lost grasp.-> R
    DP -.lost grasp.-> R
